      • addClone

        <T extends DeepCloneable> void addClone(T original,
                                        T clone)
        Register clone as the clone of original. This method must be called in the (super)constructor of clone before any of the fields get cloned using this cloner.
        Parameters:
        original - a cloneable
        clone - the clone of original
